text: Jostein Nordmoe (23 January 1895 - 1965) was a Canadian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1895 births Category:1965 deaths Category:Canadian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Canada Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:People from Målselv
